<P>Forum Features Added:</P>
<UL>
<LI>You can now sort the thread list for a forum by choosing the desired sort in the drop-down-list above the thread list table.&nbsp; The background color of the list is the same background color as your buttons.&nbsp; So if you have a texture for buttons, and didnt set your background color, you should :)</LI>
